#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.Series.nlargest.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.Series.nlargest"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nlargest.series_nlargest:1 of
msgid "Return the largest `n` elements."
msgstr "返回最大的 `n` 个元素。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nlargest.series_nlargest of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nlargest.series_nlargest:3 of
msgid "Return this many descending sorted values."
msgstr "返回此数量的降序排列的值。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nlargest.series_nlargest:5 of
msgid ""
"When there are duplicate values that cannot all fit in a Series of `n` "
"elements:  - ``first`` : return the first `n` occurrences in order     of"
" appearance. - ``last`` : return the last `n` occurrences in reverse     "
"order of appearance. - ``all`` : keep all occurrences. This can result in"
" a Series of     size larger than `n`."
msgstr ""
"当存在重复值且无法全部放入 `n` 个元素的 Series 中时：  - ``first`` : 按"
"出现顺序返回前 `n` 个。 - ``last`` : 按出现顺序的逆序返回后 `n` 个。 - ``"
"all`` : 保留所有出现的情况。这可能导致 Series 的大小超过 `n`。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nlargest.series_nlargest:5 of
msgid ""
"When there are duplicate values that cannot all fit in a Series of `n` "
"elements:"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nlargest.series_nlargest:8 of
msgid "``first`` : return the first `n` occurrences in order"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nlargest.series_nlargest:-1 of
#, fuzzy
msgid "return the first"
msgstr "返回前 `n` 行。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nlargest.series_nlargest:9 of
msgid "of appearance."
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nlargest.series_nlargest:10 of
msgid "``last`` : return the last `n` occurrences in reverse"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nlargest.series_nlargest:-1 of
#, fuzzy
msgid "return the last"
msgstr "返回最大的 `n` 个元素。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nlargest.series_nlargest:11 of
msgid "order of appearance."
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nlargest.series_nlargest:12 of
msgid "``all``"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nlargest.series_nlargest:-1 of
msgid "keep all occurrences. This can result in a Series of"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nlargest.series_nlargest:13 of
msgid "size larger than `n`."
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nlargest.series_nlargest of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nlargest.series_nlargest:16 of
msgid "The `n` largest values in the Series, sorted in decreasing order."
msgstr "Series 中最大的 `n` 个值，按降序排列。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nlargest.series_nlargest of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nlargest.series_nlargest:21 of
msgid ":py:obj:`Series.nsmallest`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nlargest.series_nlargest:22 of
msgid "Get the `n` smallest elements."
msgstr "获取最小的 `n` 个元素。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nlargest.series_nlargest:24 of
msgid ":py:obj:`Series.sort_values`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nlargest.series_nlargest:25 of
msgid "Sort Series by values."
msgstr "按值对 Series 排序。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nlargest.series_nlargest:27 of
msgid ":py:obj:`Series.head`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nlargest.series_nlargest:28 of
msgid "Return the first `n` rows."
msgstr "返回前 `n` 行。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nlargest.series_nlargest:31 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nlargest.series_nlargest:32 of
msgid ""
"Faster than ``.sort_values(ascending=False).head(n)`` for small `n` "
"relative to the size of the ``Series`` object."
msgstr ""
"对于较小的 `n` 相对于 ``Series`` 对象的大小，此方法比 ``.sort_values("
"ascending=False).head(n)`` 更快。"

